    public interface TargetDependent
extends ComponentDependent
    This is a further extension of ComponentDependent that describes an object that is dependent not only on a set of AbstractComponents and a AbstractModel but also on a set of target objects.

    This interface is similar to ComponentElement in that it includes an accessor for the object's component but in this case the interface is intended for use by PropertyEditors that require a set of parent object references that indicates what objects are actually selected to display data in a PropertySetPanel.
